org.nerd4j.csv.writer.binding

Interface ModelToCSVBinder<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - type of the data model representing the CSV record.

    public interface ModelToCSVBinder<M>
    Represents an object able to parse the data model and provide the fields of the CSV record in the right order.
    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
